**Special Containment Procedures:** There is no such thing as an SCP-[[span style="color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(0,0,0,.5)"]]6688[[/span]]. //Why// should an SCP-[[span style="color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(0,0,0,.5)"]]6688[[/span]] exist? **Description:** A thing that doesn't exist has no description.
